<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns hat der hochwirdig fürst und
              <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan>, <expan>bisch<ex>of</ex></expan> zu
                <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>, von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> brief geschikt,
            den wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>hierinn<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>slossen</expan>
<expan>send<ex>en</ex></expan>; wolten wir niht <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>, wir
                <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan> das <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> in gut zu wissen tun, daz ir ewch dest bas darinn west
            zu halten. Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
